	(1979,'【C系列4.11】函数训练之爬楼梯','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">cyn小朋友今天学会了如何爬楼梯，但她腿太短了，能走的步数不多，你能帮她算算他的走法总共有几种吗？假设有h个楼梯，一次只能走一步或者两步或者三步，求总共有几种不同的方法</span></span>\r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">第一行输入一个整数T，代表有几组测试数据。<br />\r\n接下来每行输入一个整数h(less than 30)，代表有几个楼梯。</span></span>\r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">输出有几种方法。</span></span>\r\n</p>','3\r\n10\r\n20\r\n30\r\n','274\r\n121415\r\n53798080\r\n','0','','MA, Wuyuan','','2016-12-06 20:37:15',1,32,'N',1083,1552,569,576,31.39,'','','','c'),
	(1980,'【C系列4.12】函数训练之分苹果','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">cyn小朋友所在的幼儿园今天上午的点心是苹果，但是mwy老师分到最后发现多了两个苹果，于是他决定用一种方法找出一位位幸运儿。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">n个小朋友围成一圈，编号从1-n，第一个人从1数起，数到7的那个人就被淘汰出局，接下来的人又从1数起，数到7再次被淘汰（如果人数不满7个，则循环着数）……最后剩下的一个人就是赢家（主函数已经给出）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;\r\nint jos(int n);\r\nint main()\r\n{\r\n    int n,s,t;\r\n    scanf(\"%d\",&amp;t);\r\n    while(t--)\r\n    {\r\n        scanf(\"%d\",&amp;n)\r\n        s = jos(n);\r\n        printf(\"%d \", s);\r\n    }\r\n    return 0;\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">第一行输入一个整数T,代表有T组测试样例。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">接下来的T行每行输入一个整数n(n&lt;=1000)，代表总共有几位小朋友。</span></span> \r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">对于每一个n，输出对应幸运儿的初始编号。</span></span> \r\n</p>','2\r\n100\r\n32','50\r\n5','0','','MA, Wuyuan','','2016-12-06 20:38:05',1,32,'N',898,1400,477,490,42.19,'','','','c'),
	(1981,'【C系列4.13】函数训练之组合数','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">今天cyn学会了组合数的定义，然后兴致勃勃的做好了mwy老师给的题目，你能帮她验算一下吗？（主函数已经给出，你只需要提交com函数）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;\r\nint com(int x,int y);\r\nint main()\r\n{\r\n    int a,b,t;\r\n    scanf(\"%d\",&amp;t);\r\n    while(t--)\r\n    {\r\n        scanf(\"%d %d\",&amp;a,&amp;b);\r\n        printf(\"%d\\n\",com(a,b));\r\n    }\r\n    return 0;\r\n} </code></pre>\r\n<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">第一行输入一个整数T,代表有T组测试样例</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">接下来T行每行输入两个整数n,m（n,m &lt;= 30）</span></span> \r\n</div>','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">对于每一组输入数据，输出相应的答案</span></span> \r\n</div>','4\r\n5 3\r\n6 4\r\n8 5\r\n29 15','10\r\n15\r\n56\r\n77558760','0','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;可以用递归，或者需要简化公式。\r\n</p>','MA, Wuyuan','','2016-12-06 20:38:53',1,32,'N',1195,4090,561,638,29.54,NULL,NULL,NULL,'c'),
	(1893,'杭师专属号','冬夜的杭师格外寒冷！漫漫长夜你可以做三件事。<br />\r\n1. 打代码刷题，这需要一个键盘。<br />\r\n2. 打酷炫游戏，这需要一个Watchdog2。<br />\r\n3. 享受双人温情，这需要一个懂你的女孩，喝一杯浓浓的咖啡。（注：女孩也可以和女孩一起。）<br />\r\n你有一群杭师的朋友，每个朋友都有自己的电话号码。杭师的号码由六个数字和两个\"-\"组成（例如：XX-XX-XX）。<br />\r\n如果号码上的数字都相等的话，这个号码是键盘服务。<br />\r\n如果号码上的每一位数字严格递减的话，这个号码是游戏服务。（注：看单个1位的数字）<br />\r\n另外的号码类型都是咖啡服务。<br />','第一行输入一个数字n<span style=\"color:#222222;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">(</span>1 ≤ <i>n</i> ≤ 100<span style=\"color:#222222;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">)&nbsp;</span>，代表你有n个朋友。<br />\r\n接下来有n个板块，每个板块输入格式如下：<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	第一行输入一个数字m<span style=\"color:#222222;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">(</span>0 ≤ <i>m</i>&nbsp;≤ 100<span style=\"color:#222222;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">)</span>和一个字符串（长度不超过20），代表这个朋友拥有的电话号码的数量和他的名字。\r\n</p>\r\n接下来m行，每行输入一个电话号码（格式：XX-XX-XX）。<br />','输出有三行，标点符号均为英文的标点符号。<br />\r\n第一行先输出\"If you want to have a keyboard, you should call: \"，然后输出拥有此类型号码最多的朋友的名字。<br />\r\n第二行先输出\"If you want to order a Watchdog2, you should call: \"，然后输出拥有此类型号码最多的朋友的名字。<br />\r\n第三行先输出\"If you want to have a cup of coffee with a girl, you should call: \"，然后输出拥有此类型号码最多的朋友的名字。<br />\r\n如果有多个朋友符合要求，按照输入顺序输出，两个朋友名字之间用\", \"（逗号和空格）隔开，最后一个名字后面有\".\"（句号）。注意最大值可以为0。<br />','4\r\n2 hjc\r\n22-22-22\r\n98-76-54\r\n3 lhz\r\n75-19-09\r\n23-45-67\r\n99-99-98\r\n7 ccj\r\n22-22-22\r\n11-11-11\r\n33-33-33\r\n44-44-44\r\n55-55-55\r\n66-66-66\r\n95-43-21\r\n3 hdh\r\n11-11-11\r\n99-99-99\r\n98-65-32','If you want to have a keyboard, you should call: ccj.\r\nIf you want to order a Watchdog2, you should call: hjc, ccj, hdh.\r\nIf you want to have a cup of coffee with a girl, you should call: lhz.','0','','HU, Diheng','杭州师范大学第十届程序设计竞赛','2016-12-04 13:34:29',1,128,'N',150,403,120,150,84.39,'结构体，排序','','','hznu'),
	(1074,'内部收益率','<p><!--[if !mso]>\r\n<style>\r\nv:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\no:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\nw:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning />\r\n<w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n<w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n<w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas />\r\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n<w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:SpaceForUL />\r\n<w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth />\r\n<w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone />\r\n<w:ULTrailSpace />\r\n<w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn />\r\n<w:AdjustLineHeightInTable />\r\n<w:BreakWrappedTables />\r\n<w:SnapToGridInCell />\r\n<w:WrapTextWithPunct />\r\n<w:UseAsianBreakRules />\r\n<w:DontGrowAutofit />\r\n<w:UseFELayout />\r\n</w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n</w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n</w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\ntable.MsoNormalTable\r\n{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\nmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\nmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\nmso-style-noshow:yes;\r\nmso-style-parent:\"\";\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\nmso-para-margin:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nfont-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\nmso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\nmso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">在金融中，我们有时会用内部收益率<i><span lang=\"EN-US\">IRR</span></i>来评价项目的投资财务效益，它等于使得投资净现值<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:\r\nnormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">NPV</span></i>等于<span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>的贴现率。换句话说，给定项目的期数<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span></i>、初始现金流<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF</span></i><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span></sub>和项目各期的现金流<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF</span></i><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">, <i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">CF</i><sub>2</sub>, ...</span>，<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:\r\nnormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF<sub>T</sub></span></i>，<i><span lang=\"EN-US\">IRR</span></i>是下面方程的解：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><img src=\"/OJ/admin/../upload/pimg1070_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"text-align: center; font-family: Arial;\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">为了简单起见，本题假定：除了项目启动时有一笔投入（即初始现金流<i><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF</span></i><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> &lt; 0</span>）之外，其余各期均能赚钱（即对于所有<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">i</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\">=1,2,...,<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\">T</i></span>，<i><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF</span></i><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">i</span></sub><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">&gt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span>）。根据定义，<i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">IRR</span></i>可以是负数，但不能大于<span lang=\"EN-US\">-1。</span></span></span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">输入文件最多包含</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">25</span><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">组测试数据，每个数据占两行，第一行包含一个正整数</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span></i><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">1&lt;=<i>T</i>&lt;=10</span><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">），表示项目的期数。第二行包含</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">+1</span><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">个整数：</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF</span></i><sub style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">,&nbsp;<i>CF</i><sub>1</sub>,&nbsp;<i>CF</i><sub>2</sub>, ...,&nbsp;<i>CF<sub>T</sub></i></span><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">，其中</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF</span></i><sub style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">0</span></sub><sub style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">0, 0</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&nbsp;</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">CF<sub>i</sub></span></i><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;</span></sub></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">10000 (<i>i</i>=1,2,...,<i>T</i>)</span><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">。</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">=0</span><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">表示输入结束，你的程序不应当处理这一行。</span></span></span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">对于每组数据，输出仅一行，即项目的</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">IRR</span></i><span style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">，四舍五入保留小数点后两位。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">如果</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">IRR</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">不存在，输出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&quot;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">No</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&quot;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">，如果有多个不同</span><i style=\"font-family: Arial; text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">IRR</span></i><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">满足条件，输出</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&quot;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">Too many</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">&quot;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"text-indent: 26.6666660308838px;\">（均不含引号）</span></span></span></p>','1\r\n-1 2\r\n2\r\n-8 6 9\r\n0\r\n','1.00\r\n0.50\r\n','0','','','湖南省第六届大学生计算机程序设计竞赛','2015-06-30 12:59:35',1,128,'N',34,77,14,17,97.92,'二分答案','','','hznu'),
	(1975,'【C系列4.7】函数训练之暗号','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">cyn小朋友今天参加了小学举办的侦探活动，她的任务是从暗号纸条的内容上找出特工Q给出的所有的暗号（即Q开头的单词）</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">输入一串含有空格的字符串，字符串的长度不超过300。</span></span>\r\n</p>','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">按顺序每行输出一个找到的首字母为Q或q的单词。</span></span>\r\n</div>','Queen and quick run from this site','Queen\r\nquick','0','','MA, Wuyuan','','2016-12-06 20:34:16',1,32,'N',1331,2854,634,683,21.90,'','还是scanf好用','一串字符串？不存在的','c'),
	(1976,'【C系列4.8】函数训练之被甩','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">cyn小朋友今天看了一个小故事，讲的是zp同学在大学中被各种女生甩的惨痛经历，故事上说zp在大学第一天就和一个女神级别的大一新生表白了，然后被华丽丽的拒绝了，第二天又表白了m个女生，再次被华丽丽的拒绝了m次，从那一天开始，他坚持不懈地和各种女生表白，每天表白的次数是前一天的次数加上再前一天的次数的两倍，终于在30天后被一位女生接受了，请问他在第30天被拒绝了几次？</span></span> \r\n</p>','<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">第一行有一个整数T，代表有几组测试样例。</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">接下来的T行每行有一个整数m（1 &lt;= m &lt;= 100000），代表第二天的被拒绝的次数</span></span> \r\n</div>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">对于每一个测试样例输出他被拒绝的次数p。</span></span> \r\n</p>','3\r\n1\r\n2\r\n3','357913941\r\n536870912\r\n715827883','0','<p>\r\n	&nbsp;输入，输出，请用%lld\r\n</p>','MA, Wuyuan','','2017-11-02 08:15:03',5,32,'N',1242,3258,650,681,20.70,'f','','','c'),
	(1977,'【C系列4.9】函数训练之汉诺塔问题','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">cyn小朋友今天学了汉诺塔问题，于是她想自己看看把n个盘子从a塔放到c塔，你能帮她找出方法吗？（主函数已经给出）</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">void move(int n,char c1,char c2,char c3);</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">int main()</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">{</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; int n;</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; scanf(\"%d\",&amp;n);</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; move(n,\'a\',\'b\',\'c\');</span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">}</span></span> \r\n</div>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">输入整数n（1 &lt;= n &lt;= 15）</span></span> \r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">打印出移动的最短路径，格式请看样例</span></span> \r\n</p>','3','a->c\r\na->b\r\nc->b\r\na->c\r\nb->a\r\nb->c\r\na->c','0','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">1. 关于汉诺塔问题，请自行谷歌。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">2.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family:Arial;font-size:medium;line-height:16px;\">void move(int n,char c1,char c2,char c3); 表示n个盘子从c1位置移动到c3位置，借助c2。</span></span></span> \r\n</p>','MA, Wuyuan','','2016-12-06 20:35:56',1,32,'N',999,2252,588,624,27.94,'','','','c'),
	(1978,'【C系列4.10】函数训练之全排列','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">cyn小朋友今天数学课上学到的是全排列，课后，mwy老师给了他几串字符串，你能帮cyn写出它们的全排列吗？</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">第一行输入一个整数T，表示有几组数据。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">下面每行输入一串字符串（不会出现重复字母）。</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">对于每一组数据，输出其全部排列（按字典序顺序），中间以空格间隔。</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','1\r\nabc\r\n','abc acb bac bca cab cba\r\n','0','','MA, Wuyuan','','2015-09-04 21:01:38',1,32,'N',202,755,150,213,78.11,'gtmd深搜','next_permutation','','c'),
	(1075,'Biggest Number','<p><!--[if !mso]>\r\n<style>\r\nv:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\no:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\nw:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning />\r\n<w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n<w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n<w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas />\r\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n<w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:SpaceForUL />\r\n<w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth />\r\n<w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone />\r\n<w:ULTrailSpace />\r\n<w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn />\r\n<w:AdjustLineHeightInTable />\r\n<w:BreakWrappedTables />\r\n<w:SnapToGridInCell />\r\n<w:WrapTextWithPunct />\r\n<w:UseAsianBreakRules />\r\n<w:DontGrowAutofit />\r\n<w:UseFELayout />\r\n</w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n</w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n</w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\ntable.MsoNormalTable\r\n{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\nmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\nmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\nmso-style-noshow:yes;\r\nmso-style-parent:\"\";\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\nmso-para-margin:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nfont-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\nmso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\nmso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">You have a maze </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">with</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> obstacles and </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">non-zero digits</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> in it:</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\" class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><img src=\"/OJ/admin/../upload/pimg1071_1.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">You can start from any square, walk in the maze, and finally stop at some square. </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">Each step, you may only walk into one of the <b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight:normal\"><i style=\"mso-bidi-font-style:normal\"><u>four neighbouring squares (up, down, left, right) </u></i></b>and y</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">ou cannot walk into obstacles</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> or</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">walk into</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> a square more than once. When you finish, you can get a number by writing down the digits you encounter in the same order as you </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">meet</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> them.</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">For example, you can get numbers 9784, 4832145 etc. The biggest number you can get is 791452384, shown </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">in the picture </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">above.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Your task is to find the biggest number you can get.</span></span></span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">There will be at most 25 test cases. Each test begins with two integers&nbsp;<i>R</i>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<i>C</i>&nbsp;(2&lt;=<i>R</i>,<i>C</i>&lt;=15,<i>R*C</i>&lt;=30), the number of rows and columns of the maze. </span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">The next&nbsp;<i>R</i>&nbsp;rows represent the maze. Each line contains exactly&nbsp;<i>C</i>&nbsp;characters (without leading or trailing spaces), each of them will be either \'#</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">\' or one of the nine non-zero digits.&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">There will be at least one non-obstacle squares (i.e. squares with a non-zero digit in it) in the maze.&nbsp;The input is terminated by a test case with&nbsp;<i>R</i>=<i>C</i>=0, you should not process it.</span></span></span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">For each test case, print the&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">biggest</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;number you can find, on a single line.</span></span></span></p>','3 7\r\n##9784#\r\n##123##\r\n##45###\r\n0 0\r\n','791452384\r\n','0','','','湖南省第六届大学生计算机程序设计竞赛','2015-06-30 13:01:46',1,128,'N',16,76,4,11,99.07,NULL,NULL,NULL,'hznu'),
	(1974,'【C系列4.6】函数训练之字符串逆序','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">cyn小朋友今天上英语课学到了很多新的单词，她于是她行云流水般写了一段英文小短文，但是她发现自己脑子不对，把所有的单词都写逆序了，你能帮帮她吗？</span></span> \r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">输入一行字符串（长度不超过200）</span></span> \r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">对于输入，输出每个单词逆序后的字符串。</span></span> \r\n</p>','I lliw reven reve ecnaD\r\n','I will never ever Dance\r\n','0','<p>\r\n	输入最后的换行不需要逆序。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	例如 abc\\n你需要输出的是cba\\n\r\n</p>','MA, Wuyuan','','2016-12-15 14:47:43',1,32,'N',1201,2678,587,634,27.62,'','','','c'),
	(1076,'Repairing a Road','<p><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning />\r\n<w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n<w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n<w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>2</w:DisplayVerticalDrawingGridEvery>\r\n<w:ValidateAgainstSchemas />\r\n<w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>false</w:SaveIfXMLInvalid>\r\n<w:IgnoreMixedContent>false</w:IgnoreMixedContent>\r\n<w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>false</w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText>\r\n<w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:SpaceForUL />\r\n<w:BalanceSingleByteDoubleByteWidth />\r\n<w:DoNotLeaveBackslashAlone />\r\n<w:ULTrailSpace />\r\n<w:DoNotExpandShiftReturn />\r\n<w:AdjustLineHeightInTable />\r\n<w:BreakWrappedTables />\r\n<w:SnapToGridInCell />\r\n<w:WrapTextWithPunct />\r\n<w:UseAsianBreakRules />\r\n<w:DontGrowAutofit />\r\n<w:UseFELayout />\r\n</w:Compatibility>\r\n<w:BrowserLevel>MicrosoftInternetExplorer4</w:BrowserLevel>\r\n</w:WordDocument>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=\"false\" LatentStyleCount=\"156\">\r\n</w:LatentStyles>\r\n</xml><![endif]--><!--[if gte mso 10]>\r\n<style>\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\ntable.MsoNormalTable\r\n{mso-style-name:普通表格;\r\nmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\nmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\nmso-style-noshow:yes;\r\nmso-style-parent:\"\";\r\nmso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;\r\nmso-para-margin:0cm;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nfont-size:10.0pt;\r\nfont-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:\"Times New Roman\";\r\nmso-ansi-language:#0400;\r\nmso-fareast-language:#0400;\r\nmso-bidi-language:#0400;}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">You live in a small town with <i>R</i> bidirectional roads connecting <i>C</i> crossings and you want to </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">go</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> from crossing 1 to crossing <i>C</i> as soon as possible</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">. You can visit other crossings before arriving at crossing C, but it&rsquo;s not mandatory.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">You have </span><span lang=\"EN-US\">exactly one</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> chance to ask your friend to repair exactly one existing road, <b><i><u>from the time you </u></i></b></span><b><i><u><span lang=\"EN-US\">leave</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> crossing 1</span></u></i></b><span lang=\"EN-US\">. If he repairs the <i>i</i>-th road for <i>t</i> units of time, the crossing time after that would be <i>v<sub>i</sub>a<sub>i</sub></i><sup>-<i>t</i></sup>. It\'s not difficult to see that it takes <i>v<sub>i</sub></i> units of time to cross th</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">at</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> road if your friend doesn&rsquo;t repair it.</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">You cannot start to cross the road when your friend is repairing it.</span></span></span></p>','<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">There will be at most 25 test cases. Each test case begins with two integers&nbsp;<i>C</i>&nbsp;and<i>R</i>&nbsp;(2&lt;=<i>C</i>&lt;=100, 1&lt;=<i>R</i>&lt;=500). Each of the next&nbsp;<i>R</i>&nbsp;lines contains two integers&nbsp;<i>x<sub>i</sub></i>,&nbsp;<i>y<sub>i</sub></i>(1&lt;=<i>x<sub>i</sub></i>,&nbsp;<i>y<sub>i</sub></i>&lt;=C) and two positive floating-point numbers&nbsp;<i>v<sub>i</sub></i>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<i>a<sub>i</sub></i>(1&lt;=<i>v<sub>i</sub></i>&lt;=20,1&lt;=<i>a<sub>i</sub></i>&lt;=5), indicating that there is a&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">bidirectional&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">road connecting crossing&nbsp;<i>x<sub>i</sub></i>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<i>y<sub>i</sub></i>, with parameters&nbsp;<i>v<sub>i</sub></i>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<i>a<sub>i</sub></i>&nbsp;(see above)</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">. Each pair of crossings can be connected by at most one road. The input is terminated by a test case with<i>C</i>=<i>R</i>=0, you should not process it.</span></p>','<p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">For each test case, print the smallest time it takes to reach crossing&nbsp;<i>C</i>&nbsp;from crossing&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">1</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">,&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">rounded to&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">3&nbsp;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">digits</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: medium;\">&nbsp;after decimal point. It&rsquo;s always possible to reach crossing&nbsp;<i>C</i>&nbsp;from crossing 1.</span></p>','3 2\r\n1 2 1.5 1.8\r\n2 3 2.0 1.5\r\n2 1\r\n1 2 2.0 1.8\r\n0 0\r\n','2.589\r\n1.976\r\n','0','','','湖南省第六届大学生计算机程序设计竞赛','2015-06-30 13:03:10',1,128,'N',3,10,2,3,99.53,NULL,NULL,NULL,'hznu'),
