	(1614,'三角形','<p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">将<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>，&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<span lang=\"EN-US\">,9</span>共<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>个数排成下列形态的三角形。（<span lang=\"EN-US\">30%</span>）</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; a</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; b&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; c</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; d&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; f&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; g&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; h&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; i</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextIndent\" style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;mso-layout-grid-align:\r\nnone\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">其中：<span lang=\"EN-US\">a</span>～<span lang=\"EN-US\">i</span>分别表示<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>，&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<span lang=\"EN-US\">,9</span>中的一个数字，并要求同时满足下列条件：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>（<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\">a&lt;f&lt;i;</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\">b&lt;d, g&lt;h, c&lt;e</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>（<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>）<span lang=\"EN-US\">a+b+d+f=f+g+h+i=i+e+c+a=P</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextFirstIndent2\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:81.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-81.0pt;\r\nmso-layout-grid-align:none\"></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextFirstIndent2\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:81.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-81.0pt;\r\nmso-layout-grid-align:none\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">程序要求：</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextFirstIndent2\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:81.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-81.0pt;\r\nmso-layout-grid-align:none\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span>根据输入的边长之和<span lang=\"EN-US\">P</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoBodyTextFirstIndent2\" style=\"margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;\r\nmargin-bottom:0cm;margin-left:81.0pt;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-indent:-81.0pt;\r\nmso-layout-grid-align:none\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>输出所有满足上述条件的三角形的个数。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>','','','23\r\n','2\r\n','0','<div><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">sample中满足条件的方案如下：</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 7</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp; 3&nbsp; 1&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 2&nbsp;&nbsp; 3</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp; 5&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 6&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 4</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Courier New\';\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">8&nbsp;&nbsp; 2&nbsp; 4&nbsp; 9&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 8&nbsp;&nbsp; 1&nbsp; 5&nbsp;&nbsp; 9</span></span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></div>