	(2036,'【C系列7.11】结构-11 女神历险记4(不容错过的大结局)','<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">由于</span><span style=\"color: black;\">loy</span><span style=\"color: black;\">的队伍中</span><span style=\"color: black;\">wxa</span><span style=\"color: black;\">天生神力，上回直接把密道中的一个门给掰开了，于是大家都成功的逃离了密道。根据地图，在他们前面的，就是被中国供奉了几千年的龙</span><span style=\"color: black;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">的蛋</span><span style=\"color: black;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">的壳</span><span style=\"color: black;\">&mdash;&mdash;</span><span style=\"color: black;\">的化石，</span><span style=\"color: black;\">可以说是价值连城！当然还有最后一道小小的可以轻易破解的机关，你就能拿到它了，如果事情</span><span style=\"color: black;\">发展</span><span style=\"color: black;\">的没那么快。对密道门的破坏通过一连串物理，化学，生物以及魔法反应，导致整个墓室结构被破坏，再怎么天生神力对此也没用，现在大家还有充足的时间逃离，但是又舍不得眼前的宝贝。。。。。。</span></span></span></span><span style=\"display: none;\" id=\"1435365249109E\">&nbsp;</span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"display: none;\" id=\"1435365267817S\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span style=\"color: black;\">(</span><span style=\"color: black;\">故事看完，请你帮忙</span><span style=\"color: black;\">)</span><span style=\"color: black;\">现在你拿到一张列表，列表内容如下：第一行为</span><span style=\"color: black;\">两</span><span style=\"color: black;\">个正整数</span><span style=\"color: black;\">t</span><span style=\"color: black;\">，</span><span style=\"color: black;\">n</span><span style=\"color: black;\">。其后有</span><span style=\"color: black;\">t</span><span style=\"color: black;\">行，对于每一行，有一个整数索引号</span><span style=\"color: black;\">(0~2^31)</span><span style=\"color: black;\">和字符串</span><span style=\"color: black;\">(</span><span style=\"color: black;\">长度不超过</span><span style=\"color: black;\">20)</span><span st