rial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.1818px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;\"><font face=\"Arial\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.1818px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;\"><font face=\"Arial\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; printf(&quot;NO\\n&quot;);</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.1818px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;\"><font face=\"Arial\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; }</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.1818px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;\"><font face=\"Arial\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; }</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.1818px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;\"><font face=\"Arial\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; return 0;</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18.1818px; background-color: rgb(238, 238, 238);\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: medium;\"><font face=\"Arial\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">}</font></span></div>\r\n<p></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">第一行输入一个T(T &lt;= 50)，表示有T组数据。</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">接下来T行，每行只有一个整数n（1 &lt;= n &lt;= 99999），代表你需要验证的整数。</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">对于每一个n，若是素数就输出&ldquo;YES&rdquo;，否则输出&ldquo;NO&rdquo;</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','4\r\n1\r\n2\r\n3\r\n4','NO\r\nYES\r\nYES\r\nNO','0','','ZENG, Ruiyu','2015年秋学期《程序设计基础》第四次上机考试','2016-01-12 16:38:00',1,128,'N',483,965,74,80,90.84,NULL,NULL,NULL,'hznu'),
	(1846,'WLX搬砖','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">WLX现在是人见人爱，花见花开的高富帅，左拥WJJ右抱电脑。但是人们有所不知，春风得意的他也曾有着一段艰苦的奋斗史。<br />\r\n那时，WLX为了给WJJ买生日礼物，在某建筑工地搬砖挣钱。工地上运来一卡车砖，包工头CYP让WLX把砖卸下，并把一块快分开（要求任何2块砖都要分开）。作为资深搬砖工，WLX总是每次将一堆砖分为两堆，这时候，所消耗的体力是分完之后两堆砖数目的差值。<br />\r\n已知卡车运来的砖数目，请计算出WLX完成任务所需的最小体力。（主函数代码部分已经固定，请按需写函数部分）</span></span>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		#include&lt;stdio.h&gt;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		int fun(int n);\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		int main()\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		{\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; int T;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; scanf(\"%d\", &amp;T);\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; while(T--)\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; {\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; int n;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\"> </span>scanf(\"%d\", &amp;n);\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; printf(\"%d\r\n\", fun(n));\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; }\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		&nbsp; &nbsp; return 0;\r\n	</div>\r\n	<div>\r\n		}\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">输入数据第一行是一个正整数T（T&lt;=100），表示有T组测试数据。<br />\r\n接下来T行每行一个正整数N（N&lt;=10000000），表示卡车运来的砖块数目。</span></span>\r\n</p>','<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:medium;\"><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">对于每组数据，请输出WLX完成任务所需的最少体力数。</span></span>\r\n</p>','3\r\n3\r\n7984715\r\n6563104','1\r\n1495412\r\n2670304','0','','LI, Heng','2015年秋学期《程序设计基础》第四次上机考试','2018-07-01 09:01:51',5,128,'N',72,108,15,15,98.10,NULL,NULL,NULL,'hznu'),
	(1847,'统计成绩','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">又到了期末考试，胡老师又开始头疼统计成绩，请你设计一个程序来帮助他统计学生成绩。</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">输入一个整数T 代表接下来有T行输入（&lt;=10000）</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">每行输入四个数据，第一个数字代表班级（整数，取值范围1-10000），第二个整数为他的学号( 整数，取值范围1-100000)，第三个字符串代表名字 ( 长度&lt;= 4)，&nbsp;&nbsp;第四个数字为他的成绩(整数，数值&lt;= 100)。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">接下来有多组输入（不超过10000组）</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">输入一个整数K，按照学号从小到大输出班级K的学生成绩，每行输出一名学生姓名和成绩，中间用空格隔开（若某一学号对应的学生信息没有输入则不用输出,若班级里没有任何学生记录则不用输出）</span></p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">对于每个班级k，分行输出这个班级的所有同学的信息，每个同学的信息包括姓名和成绩，姓名和成绩以一个空格隔开。</span></span></p>\r\n<p></p>','5\r\n4 5 ds 12\r\n1 9999 as 9\r\n9999 1 ef 99\r\n20 50 we 45\r\n23 56 er 89\r\n4\r\n1\r\n1\r\n9999\r\n','ds 12\r\nas 9\r\nas 9\r\nef 99\r\n','0','<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">注意：（1）必须使用链表，不然极有可能出现TLE或MLE；</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （2）使用数组来存储链表头。&nbsp;</span></span></div>\r\n<div><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; （3）注意本题的时间限制和内存限制</span></span></div>','LI, Heng','2015年秋学期《程序设计基础》第四次上机考试','2016-01-13 01:04:27',1,8,'N',15,58,7,10,98.85,NULL,NULL,NULL,'hznu'),
