=\"EN-US\">n</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">. You can also get the sequence S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">n+1</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> using the same method and so on.&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">\r\n<p style=\"text-indent:21.0pt\" class=\"MsoNormal\"></p>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\">  </span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">For example,S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> = 1,1.Since 1 + 1 = 2, we will insert 2 between two 1s and then we get S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">, S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> = 1,2,1. Now we will insert two 3s in the sequence to get S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">, as you can see, S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> = 1,3,2,3,1. In the same way, we know S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\"> = 1,4,3,2,3,4,1, S5 = 1,5,4,3,5,2,5,3,4,5,1 and so on. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Here the question comes: give you n, you will be asked to output the number of n in S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">n</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">. For example if n = 5, you will output 4 since there are 4 5s in S</span><sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span></sub><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></span></span></span></p>','<p><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial;\"><!--[if gte mso 9]><xml>\r\n<w:WordDocument>\r\n<w:View>Normal</w:View>\r\n<w:Zoom>0</w:Zoom>\r\n<w:TrackMoves />\r\n<w:TrackFormatting />\r\n<w:PunctuationKerning />\r\n<w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>7.8 磅</w:DrawingGridVerticalSpacing>\r\n<w:DisplayHorizontalDrawingGridEvery>0</w: